<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Family Invitation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      margin: 10px 10px 10px 0;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .accept-button {
      background-color: #22c55e;
    }
    .decline-button {
      background-color: #ef4444;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>You've Been Invited to Join a Family!</h1>
  </div>

  <p>Hi <%= @user.name || @user.username %>,</p>

  <p><strong><%= @inviter.name || @inviter.username %></strong> has invited you to join their family "<strong><%= @family.name %></strong>" on our recipe sharing platform.</p>

  <% if @family.description.present? %>
    <p><em><%= @family.description %></em></p>
  <% end %>

  <p>As a family member, you'll be able to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Access shared family cookbooks</li>
    <li>Add your own recipes to the family collection</li>
    <li>Browse and cook from family recipes</li>
    <li>Collaborate on meal planning</li>
  </ul>

  <p>Would you like to join this family?</p>

  <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
    <%= link_to "Accept Invitation", @accept_url, class: "button accept-button" %>
    <%= link_to "Decline", @decline_url, class: "button decline-button" %>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>This invitation will expire in 30 days. If you're not interested, you can simply ignore this email.</p>
    <p>If you have any questions, please contact <%= @inviter.email %>.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>